	<p>AlumniFidelity, Inc. (“AlumniFidelity”) knows that you care how information about you is used and shared, and we appreciate your trust that we will do so carefully and sensibly. This notice describes our privacy policy. This policy covers how AlumniFidelity treats personal information that it collects and receives, including information related to your past use of its services. This policy does not apply to the practices of companies or entities that AlumniFidelity does not own or control, or to people that AlumniFidelity does not employ or manage. For purposes of this policy, “personal information” is information about you that is personally identifiable like your name, address, email address, or phone number, and that is not otherwise public information. By visiting AlumniFidelity, you are accepting the practices described in this Privacy Notice.</p>

	<h2>What Personal Information About Customers Does AlumniFidelity Gather?</h2>

